# ── Build outputs ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
bin/
obj/
out/
publish/
**/publish/
artifacts/

# ── .NET / IDE ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.dll
*.exe
*.pdb
*.cache
*.user
*.suo
.vs/
.idea/
*.nupkg

# ── Runtime data (per-account SQLite store — not source) ─────────────────────
*.db
*.db-wal
*.db-shm

# ── Dev TLS certs (regenerate locally) ───────────────────────────────────────
*.pfx
**/mqel-ca.pem
**/envcheck.txt

# ── Captured client traffic (may contain Steam auth tickets / PII) ───────────
**/captures/

# ── Logs / scratch ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
*.log
**/*.log

# ── Game data — Ubisoft's copyrighted assets, NEVER committed. Supply your own.
/game-data/

# ── OS ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
